trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Control.PreviewKeyDown"></xref> event.
For more information about handling events, see [Events](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.PreviewKeyDownEventArgs"></xref> class with the specified key.
One of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Keys"></xref> values.
Gets a value indicating whether the ALT key was pressed.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the ALT key was pressed; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Gets a value indicating whether the CTRL key was pressed.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the CTRL key was pressed; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Gets or sets a value indicating whether a key is a regular input key.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the key is a regular input key; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Gets the keyboard code for a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Control.KeyDown"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Control.KeyUp"></xref> event.
One of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Keys"></xref> values.
Gets the key data for a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Control.KeyDown"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Control.KeyUp"></xref> event.
One of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Keys"></xref> values.
Gets the keyboard value for a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Control.KeyDown"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Control.KeyUp"></xref> event.
An <xref:System.Int32> representing the keyboard value.
Gets the modifier flags for a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Control.KeyDown"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Control.KeyUp"></xref> event.
One of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Keys"></xref> values.
Gets a value indicating whether the SHIFT key was pressed.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the SHIFT key was pressed; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
